headline: Is Mosaic Stock Set for a Rebound After Recent 14% Pullback in 2025?
summary: Wondering what your next move should be with Mosaic stock? You are not alone. If you have been watching this company for any length of time, you have probably noticed the recent rollercoaster ride. After a solid year-to-date gain of 20.3%, the stock has taken a bit of a breather over the past month, dipping 14.2%. Pull back further and you see that five-year holders are still up by an impressive 72.9%, but the longer three-year stretch paints a less rosy picture, with shares down over 40.2%...
